{
  "stem": "7069.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because, pretty soon, we ourselves didn't know what we had more on our bodies, whether it was lice, fleas, or bed bugs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All these things tried to feast on your body.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you had this all over your body.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And just imagine, like some people who have one lousy mosquito bite and they can't resist.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Imagine you have this all over your body, and particularly children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Again, talking about children, they were much more vulnerable to this than even an, even an-- an adult.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so this was the first thing that we noticed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then, of course, soon we were, we were assigned to workplaces.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was, at first, outside the camp, digging ditches for new drainage, for new water coming in, new pipes laying and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In fact, with this food that I described, we were very, very much looking for other food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "At one time, for a stretch of a couple or three days, we had to dig these ditches in the middle through a tomato field where they were-- tomatoes were grown.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were already ripe on the vine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, of course, once in a while when we, when we when we had to make sure that the guard didn't look, we would pick them and would quickly swallow 'em.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, and then also now we were trying to get-- this would be wonderful to get it into the camp somehow for our wives.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My brother was married then to his wife, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, and not wives, our mother-- in, in case, our mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we tried to figure out how to smuggle them in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because we were always frisked when we came through the gate into the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They came down with their hands.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
